net.minecraftforge.fluids.capability.templates

类 FluidHandlerFluidMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.minecraftforge.fluids.capability.templates.FluidHandlerFluidMap
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    IFluidHandler

    public class FluidHandlerFluidMap
extends java.lang.Object
implements IFluidHandler
    FluidHandlerFluidMap is a template class for concatenating multiple handlers into one, where each handler is associated with a different fluid.

      • drain

        public FluidStack drain(int maxDrain,
                        boolean doDrain)
        从接口复制的说明: IFluidHandler
        Drains fluid out of internal tanks, distribution is left entirely to the IFluidHandler.

        This method is not Fluid-sensitive.

        指定者:
        drain 在接口中 IFluidHandler
        参数:
        maxDrain - Maximum amount of fluid to drain.
        doDrain - If false, drain will only be simulated.
        返回:
        FluidStack representing the Fluid and amount that was (or would have been, if simulated) drained.
